For consistency, this template uses the same colours as those used in {{tl|Infobox religious building}} as far as possible: see [[Template:Infobox religious building/doc#Automatic coloring]].

When darker colours are used, the heading text is rendered in white by the template {{tl|Infobox church/font color}}.

Before changing the colours in this template, or inserting new denominations and colours, please discuss the matter with other editors at "[[Template talk:Infobox church]]". Thanks.